                            <h3 class="text-justify">3). Pack Some Less and Save Some More! </h3>
                            <p class="text-justify">When you pack some less, then you can save some more and that’s impressive for you to make sure affordable travel package of SAS Airlines Booking. Baggage fee or the checked baggage fee always affects your total budget and you can also save your time for boarding if you are only travelling with the carry-on baggage. Also, read the SAS Airlines Baggage Policy before fly to make sure that you followed weight and dimensions rules.  </p>
